msgctxt "1024"
msgid "Train your apprentices and have them win the tournament within 50 turns! The sooner they win, the better the prize money and evaluation."
msgstr "¡Entrena a tus aprendices y haz que ganen torneos dentro de 50 turnos! Cuanto antes gane, mayor será la recompensa y la evaluación."

msgctxt "1816"
msgid "Train your apprentices and have them win the tournament <Color:7>within 50 turns<Color:Default>! The sooner they win, the better the prize money and the evaluation."
msgstr "¡Entrena a tus aprendices y haz que ganen torneos <Color:7>dentro de 50 turnos<Color:Default>! Cuanto antes gane, mayor será la recompensa y la evaluación."

msgctxt "1828"
msgid "You can earn the most prize money by having your apprentice win <Color:7>within 15 turns<Color:Default>. After that, the amount will start to decrease every five turns."
msgstr "Obtendrás el premio mayor si tu aprendiz gana <Color:7>dentro de 15 turnos<Color:Default>. De ahí en adelante, el premio disminuirá cada 5 turnos."

msgctxt "1840"
msgid "Train your apprentices efficiently so they are able to win in as few turns as possible."
msgstr "Entrena a tus aprendices eficientemente para hacerlos capaces de ganar en la menor cantidad de turnos posibles."

